## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of sources primarily focused on the U.S. context, potentially overlooking the roles of immigrants in other regions during the same period. Additionally, the reliance on secondary sources may introduce biases inherent in the original analyses. Further research could benefit from primary historical documents and a broader geographical scope.